[SN]TITLE[SN]
Police appeal to trace bloodstained man

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Police in Forth Valley are appealing for information after receiving reports of a bloodstained man at a layby on the A84.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The man was seen at the canoeists' layby between Callander and Buchany at about 19:30 on Saturday.
Officers said the man had blood on his face and shirt.
Police Scotland said it believed the man may have been injured and wanted to trace him in order to check on his welfare.
